---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Sverige Personnummer Input
description: an input for entering Sweden's Personnummer
---

{% from "components/sverige-personnummer-input/macro.njk" import sverigePersonnummerInput %}
{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/field/macro.njk" import field %}

<h2>Default</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "sverige-personnummer-input-demo", text: "Personal Identity Number" }) }}
  {{ sverigePersonnummerInput({ id: "sverige-personnummer-input-demo" }) }}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>12 digits in the format CCYYMMDDZZZQ: CCYYMMDD is the date of birth, ZZZ a serial (odd male, even female), and Q a Luhn check digit.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personal_identity_number_(Sweden)">Personal Identity Number</a>.</p>
